 players comprising four nationalities. [[Maurice Malpas]] featured in all but one of United's 60 matches. The table below shows the number of appearances and goals scored by each player.<ref name=\"stats\">{{cite web|url=http://www.dirtyarab.pwp.blueyonder.co.uk/History/1987s/1987-90/88-88page.htm|title=1987\u201388|work=Glenrothes Arabs|accessdate=4 February 2008}} {{Dead link|date=October 2010|bot=H3llBot}}</ref>\n{{Extended football squad start|[[Scottish Premier Division]]|Tennent's [[Scottish Cup]]|[[Scottish League Cup|Skol Cup]]|[[UEFA Cup Winners' Cup]]}}\n{{Extended football squad player|no=|name=[[Alan Main]]|pos=GK|nat=Scotland|8|0|2|0|0|0|0|0}}\n{{Extended football squad player|no=|name=[[Billy Thomson]]|pos=GK|nat=Scotland|36|0|7|0|3|0|4|0}}\n{{Extended football squad player|no=|name=[[Dave Beaumont]]|pos=DF|nat=Scotland|9|1|0|0|0|0|2|0}}\n{{Extended football squad player|no=|name=[[John Clark (footballer born 1964)|John Clark]]|pos=DF|nat=Scotland|27|3|7|0|0|0|3|2}}\n{{Extended football squad player|no=|name=[[Alex Cleland]]|pos=DF|nat=Scotland|1|0|0|0|0|0|0|0}}\n{{Extended football squad player|no=|name=[[Paul Hegarty]]|pos=DF|nat=Scotland|41|1|9|1|3|0|4|0}}\n{{Extended football squad player|no=|name=[[John Holt (footballer, born 1956)|John Holt]]|pos=DF|nat=Scotland|6|0|0|0|3|0|0|0}}\n{{Extended football squad player|no=|name=[[Gary McGinnis]]|pos=DF|nat=Scotland|10|0|1|0|0|0|4|0}}\n{{Extended football squad player|no=|name=[[Maurice Malpas]]|pos=DF|nat=Scotland|44|0|8|1|3|1|4|0}}\n{{Extended football squad player|no=|name=[[Dave Narey]]|pos=DF|nat=Scotland|39|0|9|0|3|0|3|0}}\n{{Extended football squad player|no=|name=[[Brian Welsh]]|pos=DF|nat=Scotland|1|1|0|0|0|0|0|0}}\n{{Extended football squad player|no=|name=[[Eamonn Bannon]]|pos=MF|nat=Scotland|26|1|9|4|2|0|3|0}}\n{{Extended football squad player|no=|name=[[David Bowman (footballer born 1964)|Dave Bowman]]|pos=MF|nat=Scotland|38|1|8|0|2|0|3|0}}\n{{Extended football squad player|no=|name=[[Harry Curran]]|pos=MF|nat=Scotland|6|0|0|0|0|0|0|0}}\n{{Extended football squad player|no=|name=[[Alan Irvine (footballer born 1958)|Alan Irvine]]|pos=MF|nat=Scotland|16|2|1|2|1|0|1|0}}\n{{Extended football squad player|no=|name=[[Paul Kinnaird]]|pos=MF|nat=Scotland|11|0|0|0|0|0|2|0}}\n{{Extended football squad player|no=|name=[[Billy Kirkwood]]|pos=MF|nat=Scotland|1|0|0|1|0|0|0|0}}\n{{Extended football squad player|no=|name=[[Jim McInally]]|pos=MF|nat=Scotland|36|2|9|0|0|0|1|0}}\n{{Extended football squad player|no=|name=[[Billy McKinlay]]|pos=MF|nat=Scotland|12|1|0|0|0|0|1|0}}\n{{Extended football squad player|no=|name=[[Gordon McLeod (footballer)|Gordon McLeod]]|pos=MF|nat=Scotland|12|3|0|0|0|0|1|0}}\n{{Extended football squad player|no=|name=[[Joe McLeod]]|pos=MF|nat=Scotland|10|1|3|1|0|0|1|0}}\n{{Extended football squad player|no=|name=[[Ian McPhee]]|pos=MF|nat=Scotland|10|1|3|0|1|1|0|0}}\n{{Extended football squad player|no=|name=[[Allan Preston]]|pos=MF|nat=Scotland|2|0|0|0|0|0|0|0}}\n{{Extended football squad player|no=|name=[[Ian Redford]]|pos=MF|nat=Scotland|25|6|8|2|3|0|2|0}}\n{{Extended football squad player|no=|name=[[Iain Ferguson]]|pos=FW|nat=Scotland|38|11|8|2|3|2|3|1}}\n{{Extended football squad player|no=|name=[[Hamish French]]|pos=FW|nat=Scotland|20|3|5|1|0|0|1|0}}\n{{Extended football squad player|no=|name=[[Kevin Gallacher]]|pos=FW|nat=Scotland|26|3|8|3|1|2|1|0}}\n{{Extended football squad player|no=|name=[[Alan Irvine (footballer born 1962)|Alan Irvine]]|pos=FW|nat=Scotland|7|0|0|0|1|0|0|0}}\n{{Extended football squad player|no=|name=[[Mixu Paatelainen]]|pos=FW|nat=Finland|19|9|8|2|0|0|0|0}}\n{{Extended football squad player|no=|name=[[Paul Sturrock]]|pos=FW|nat=Scotland|9|3|0|0|3|2|3|2}}\n|}\n\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-2}}\n\n===Goalscorers===\nUnited had 19 players score with the team scoring 83 goals in total. The top goalscorer was [[Iain Ferguson]], who finished the season with 16 goals.<ref name=\"autogenerated1\">{{cite web|url=http://www.dirtyarab.pwp.blueyonder.co.uk/History/1987s/1987-88/87-88page.htm|title=1987\u201388|work=Glenrothes Arabs|accessdate=6 February 2008}} {{Dead link|date=October 2010|bot=H3llBot}}</ref>\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:center; font-size:95%\"\n|-\n!Name!!League!!Cups!!Total\n|-\n|{{left}}{{sortname|Iain|Ferguson}}||11||5||{{goal}} '''16'''\n|-\n|{{left}}{{sortname|Mixu|Paatelainen}}||9||2||{{goal}} '''11'''\n|-\n|{{left}}{{sortname|Ian|Redford}}||6||2||{{goal}} {{0}}'''8'''\n|-\n|{{left}}{{sortname|Paul|Sturrock}}||3||4||{{goal}} {{0}}'''7'''\n|-\n|{{left}}{{sortname|Kevin|Gallacher}}||3||3||{{goal}} {{0}}'''6'''\n|-\n|{{left}}{{sortname|John|Clark|John Clark (footballer born 1964)}}||3||2||{{goal}} {{0}}'''5'''\n|-\n|{{left}}{{sortname|Eamonn|Bannon}}||1||4||{{goal}} {{0}}'''5'''\n|-\n|{{left}}{{sortname|Hamish|French}}||3||1||{{goal}} {{0}}'''4'''\n|-\n|{{left}}{{sortname|Alan|Irvine|Alan Irvine (footballer born 1958)}}||2||2||{{goal}} {{0}}'''4'''\n|-\n|{{left}}{{sortname|Gordon|McLeod|Gordon McLeod (footballer)}}||3||0||{{goal}} {{0}}'''3'''\n|-\n|{{left}}''{{sortname|Own|goals|Own goal}}''||3||0||{{goal}} {{0}}'''3'''\n|-\n|{{left}}{{sortname|Jim|McInally}}||2||0||{{goal}} {{0}}'''2'''\n|-\n|{{left}}{{sortname|Paul|Hegarty}}||1||1||{{goal}} {{0}}'''2'''\n|-\n|{{left}}{{sortname|Joe|McLeod}}||1||1||{{goal}} {{0}}'''2'''\n|-\n|{{left}}{{sortname|Ian|McPhee}}||1||1||{{goal}} {{0}}'''2'''\n|-\n|{{left}}{{sortname|Maurice|Malpas}}||0||2||{{goal}} {{0}}'''2'''\n|-\n|{{left}}{{sortname|Dave|Beaumont}}||1||0||{{goal}} {{0}}'''1'''\n|-\n|{{left}}{{sortname|Dave|Bowman|David Bowman (footballer born 1964)}}||1||0||{{goal}} {{0}}'''1'''\n|-\n|{{left}}{{sortname|Billy|McKinlay}}||1||0||{{goal}} {{0}}'''1'''\n|-\n|{{left}}{{sortname|Brian|Welsh}}||1||0||{{goal}} {{0}}'''1'''\n|}\n{{col-2}}\n\n===Discipline===\nDuring the 1987\u201388 season, two United players were sent off. Statistics for cautions are unavailable.<ref name=\"autogenerated2\">{{cite web|url=htt