k (footballer born 1964)|Clark]]\n|- style=\"background:#efe;\"\n| {{left}}28 October 1987 ||{{left}}[[Hibernian F.C.|Hibernian]]||[[Easter Road|A]]||1\u20130||9,250||{{left}}[[Billy McKinlay|McKinlay]]\n|- style=\"background:#fee;\"\n| {{left}}31 October 1987 ||{{left}}[[St Mirren F.C.|St Mirren]]||[[Tannadice Park|H]]||2\u20133||7,607||{{left}}[[Iain Ferguson|Ferguson]], [[Mixu Paatelainen|Paatelainen]]\n|- style=\"background:#fee;\"\n| {{left}}7 November 1987 ||{{left}}[[Motherwell F.C.|Motherwell]]||[[Fir Park|A]]||1\u20132||2,927||{{left}}[[Iain Ferguson|Ferguson]]\n|- style=\"background:#efe;\"\n| {{left}}14 November 1987 ||{{left}}[[Dunfermline Athletic F.C.|Dunfermline]]||[[Tannadice Park|H]]||1\u20130||8,699||{{left}}[[Mixu Paatelainen|Paatelainen]]\n|- style=\"background:#fee;\"\n| {{left}}18 November 1987 ||{{left}}[[Heart of Midlothian F.C.|Hearts]]||[[Tannadice Park|H]]||0\u20133||14,258||\n|- style=\"background:#efe;\"\n| {{left}}21 November 1987 ||{{left}}[[Greenock Morton F.C.|Morton]]||[[Cappielow|A]]||1\u20130||3,000||{{left}}[[Iain Ferguson|Ferguson]]\n|- style=\"background:#fee;\"\n| {{left}}24 November 1987 ||{{left}}[[Falkirk F.C.|Falkirk]]||[[Brockville Park|A]]||1\u20134||4,000||{{left}}[[Gordon McLeod (footballer)|G McLeod]]\n|- style=\"background:#fee;\"\n| {{left}}28 November 1987 ||{{left}}[[Dundee F.C.|Dundee]]||[[Tannadice Park|H]]||1\u20133||13,625||{{left}}[[John Clark (footballer born 1964)|Clark]]\n|- style=\"background:#fee;\"\n| {{left}}5 December 1987 ||{{left}}[[Rangers F.C.|Rangers]]||[[Ibrox Stadium|A]]||0\u20131||41,159||\n|- style=\"background:#efe;\"\n| {{left}}12 December 1987 ||{{left}}[[Motherwell F.C.|Motherwell]]||[[Tannadice Park|H]]||3\u20131||5,703||{{left}}[[Gordon McLeod (footballer)|G McLeod]], [[Mixu Paatelainen|Paatelainen]], [[Iain Ferguson|Ferguson]]\n|- style=\"background:#fee;\"\n| {{left}}16 December 1987 ||{{left}}[[Hibernian F.C.|Hibernian]]||[[Tannadice Park|H]]||1\u20132||6,095||{{left}}[[Iain Ferguson