ren F.C.|St Mirren]]||[[Tannadice Park|H]]||5\u20131||6,294||{{left}}[[David Bowman (footballer born 1964)|Bowman]], [[Iain Ferguson|Ferguson]], [[Hamish French|French]], [[Alan Irvine (footballer born 1958)|Irvine]] (2)\n|- style=\"background:#efe;\"\n| {{left}}2 April 1988 ||{{left}}[[Dundee F.C.|Dundee]]||[[Tannadice Park|H]]||1\u20130||13,874||{{left}}[[Hamish French|French]]\n|- style=\"background:#fee;\"\n| {{left}}16 April 1988 ||{{left}}[[Motherwell F.C.|Motherwell]]||[[Fir Park|A]]||2\u20134||3,822||{{left}}[[John Clark (footballer born 1964)|Clark]], [[Joe McLeod|J McLeod]]\n|- style=\"background:#ffe;\"\n| {{left}}23 April 1988 ||{{left}}[[Dunfermline Athletic F.C.|Dunfermline]]||[[Tannadice Park|H]]||2\u20132||8,263||{{left}}[[Jim McInally|McInally]], [[Iain Ferguson|Ferguson]]\n|- style=\"background:#efe;\"\n| {{left}}30 April 1988 ||{{left}}[[Greenock Morton F.C.|Morton]]||[[Cappielow|A]]||4\u20130||2,000||{{left}}[[Mixu Paatelainen|Paatelainen]] (4)\n|- style=\"background:#efe;\"\n| {{left}}4 May 1988 ||{{left}}[[Falkirk F.C.|Falkirk]]||[[Brockville Park|A]]||2\u20131||4,500||{{left}}[[Brian Welsh|Welsh]], [[Kevin Gallacher|Gallacher]]\n|- style=\"background:#ffe;\"\n| {{left}}7 May 1988 ||{{left}}[[Heart of Midlothian F.C.|Hearts]]||[[Tannadice Park|H]]||0\u20130||9,820||\n|}\n\n===Scottish Cup===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"font-size:95%; text-align:center\"\n|-\n!Date!!Opponent!!Venue!!Result!!Attendance!!Scorers\n|- style=\"background:#efe;\"\n| {{left}}30 January 1988 ||{{left}}[[Arbroath F.C.|Arbroath]]||[[Gayfield Park|A]]||7\u20130||5,905||{{left}}[[Maurice Malpas|Malpas]], [[Eamonn Bannon|Bannon]], [[Alan Irvine (footballer born 1958)|Irvine]] (2), [[Mixu Paatelainen|Paatelainen]]<br />[[Hamish French|French]], [[Ian Redford|Redford]]\n|- style=\"background:#efe;\"\n| {{left}}20 February 1988 ||{{left}}[[Airdrieonians F.C. (1878)|Airdrieonians]]||[[Broomfield Park|A]]||2\u20130||6,727||{{left}}[[Paul Hegarty|Hegarty]], [[Eamonn Bannon|Bannon]]\n|- style=\"background:#ffe;\"\n| {{left}}12 March 1988 ||{{left}}[[Dundee F.C.|Dundee]]||[[Dens Park|A]]||0\u20130||19,355||\n|- style=\"background:#ffe;\"\n| {{left}}15 March 1988 ||{{left}}[[Dundee F.C.|Dundee]]||[[Tannadice Park|H]]||2\u20132||17,055||{{left}}[[Eamonn Bannon|Bannon]] (2)\n|- style=\"background:#efe;\"\n| {{left}}28 March 1988 ||{{left}}[[Dundee F.C.|Dundee]]||[[Dens Park|A]]||3\u20130||19,152||{{left}}[[Ian Redford|Redford]], [[Iain Ferguson|Ferguson]], [[Joe McLeod|McLeod]]\n|- style=\"background:#ffe;\"\n| {{left}}9 April 1988 ||{{left}}[[Aberdeen F.C.|Aberdeen]]||[[Hampden Park|N]]||0\u20130||20,488||\n|- style=\"background:#ffe;\"\n| {{left}}13 April 1988 ||{{left}}[[Aberdeen F.C.|Aberdeen]]||[[Hampden Park|N]]||1\u20131||17,288||{{left}}[[Mixu Paatelainen|Paatelainen]]\n|- style=\"background:#efe;\"\n| {{left}}20 April 1988 ||{{left}}[[Aberdeen F.C.|Aberdeen]]||[[Hampden Park|N]]||1\u20130||19,048||{{left}}[[Iain Ferguson|Ferguson]]\n|- style=\"background:#fee;\"\n| {{left}}14 May 1988 ||{{left}}[[Celtic F.C.|Celtic]]||[[Hampden Park|N]]||1\u20132||74,000||{{left}}[[Kevin Gallacher|Gallacher]]\n|}\n\n===Skol Cup===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"font-size:95%; text-align:center\"\n|-\n!Date!!Opponent!!Venue!!Result!!Attendance!!Scorers\n|- style=\"background:#efe;\"\n| {{left}}19 August 1987 ||{{left}}[[Partick Thistle F.C.|Partick Thistle]]||[[Tannadice Park|H]]||2\u20130||6,075||{{left}}[[Ian McPhee|McPhee]], [[Iain Ferguson|Ferguson]], [[Kevin Gallacher|Gallacher]], [[Paul Sturrock|Sturrock]]\n|- style=\"background:#efe;\"\n| {{left}}25 August 1987 ||{{left}}[[Raith Rovers F.C.|Raith Rovers]]||[[Starks Park|A]]||2\u20131||6,500||{{left}}[[Paul Sturrock|Sturrock]], [[Maurice Malpas|Malpas]]\n|- style=\"background:#fee;\"\n| {{left}}2 September 1987 ||{{left}}[[Dundee F.C.|Dundee]]||[[Firhill Stadium|A]]||2\u20130||19,817||{{left}}[[Iain Ferguson|Ferguson]]\n|}\n\n===UEFA Cup===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" sty